[Term]
id: elmo:3620029
name: mammal trapping process
def: "A mechanical fauna control process in which a human uses traps to control fauna." [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trapping]
is_a: elmo:3620028 ! mechanical fauna control process
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4366-3088
