[Term]
id: elmo:3620031
name: fencing process
def: "A mechanical fauna control process in which a human installs fencing to restrict either immigration or emmigration of fauna from a particular area." [doi:10.1016/j.biocon.2017.08.001]
is_a: elmo:3620067 ! fauna exclusion process
