[Term]
id: elmo:3620032
name: mechanical species deterrent process
def: "A mechanical fauna control process in which a human installs an electronic device to deter species from a particular area." [doi:10.1111/jfb.13769]
is_a: elmo:3620028 ! mechanical fauna control process
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4366-3088
