[Term]
id: elmo:3620033
name: mechanical hydrological alteration process
def: "A mechanical ecosystem management process during which a human deliberately alters the hydrologic cycle in an area." [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Water_cycle]
is_a: elmo:3620020 ! mechanical ecosystem management process
property_value: dcterms:contributor https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4366-3088
