[Term]
id: elmo:3620040
name: buffer strip creation process
def: "A mechanical ecosystem management process in which a human establishes strips of vegetation between landscape features such as agricultural fields and watercourses, using earthworks and planting processes." [doi:10.2134/jeq2018.03.0120]
is_a: elmo:3620020 ! mechanical ecosystem management process
